## File Structure

```
scraping/
├── ALL_PROVIDERS_CONSOLIDATED.csv    ← Start here for data
├── MASTER_REPORT.md                  ← Start here for analysis
├── README.md                         ← Start here for overview
├── QUICK_REFERENCE.md               ← This file
│
├── Provider Catalogs (7 × 3 = 21 files)
│   ├── {provider}_catalog.json
│   ├── {provider}_catalog.csv
│   └── {provider}_report.md
│
├── Scripts (reproducible)
│   ├── analyze_providers.py
│   ├── scrape_all_providers.py
│   └── scrape_targeted.py
│
└── Metadata
    ├── final_summary.json
    └── provider_analysis.json
```

